=== SESSION PATCH NOTES [SESSION 5 — THE HELIOS WING GAMBIT] ===
[Legacy Note: Following Session 4: Ko.Bun.Maru Heist. Maintains narrative and temporal continuity.]
────────────────────────────────
UPDATED_LINES:
- VITALS: Karma 37 -> 45. Nuyen 132,405¥ -> 137,405¥. Condition: Full Health (0P, 0S).
- REPUTATION MATRIX:
  * Shiawase Corporation: Enemy (-4) -> Focused Enemy (-5).
  * The Silencers: Lethal (-5) -> [NEUTRALIZED].
  * Charter Protocol: Unknown (?) -> Active Adversary (-4).
  * NEW: The Spikers: Contractual Ally (+2).
- GEAR: ADDED - 2x Ares Sigma-3 Assault Rifles w/ gas grenade launchers, 4x spare gas grenade mags, 3x high-capacity power cells, 1x Silencer armored suit (worn), 1x Hardened Extraction Case (contains Sunspot Core), 1x Resonance Stabilizer - Theta Class, 1x R6 Maglock Passkey, 1x R5 Directional Jammer, 1x Hardened Tool Kit (R6), Silencer Commlink & Datachips (encrypted), Charter Protocol Server Node (partially decrypted).
- THREADS:
  * #1 The Ghost in the Machine [ACTIVE/CRITICAL] -> [IMMINENT DECISION].
  * #11 The Silencers [ACTIVE/IMMINENT] -> [RESOLVED/NEUTRALIZED].
  * NEW #17: [CHARTER'S CURATOR] [ACTIVE/AGGRESSIVE].
  * NEW #18: [THE SUNSPIRE SEEDLING] [ACTIVE/ENTROPIC].
  * NEW #19: [THE SPIKER PACT] [ACTIVE/STABILIZING].
- TIMERS:
  * Scrambler Completion: [COMPLETE/READY].
  * The Silencers Heist: [RESOLVED/FAILED (FOR THEM)].
  * Rent Due: 26 days.
  * Spiker Contract: 14 days remaining.

NARRATIVE_SUMMARY:
Anchor and Stormbreak executed a near-flawless counter-heist against The Silencers at the Shiawase Atrium's Helios Wing, securing the Sunspot Core and a Resonance Stabilizer. In a defining act of mercy, Anchor chose not to purge a contained metaphysical entity (Project Sunspire 'Seedling'), allowing it to breach. The team escaped utilizing the newly contracted Spiker gang, forging them into a capable asset. The Silencers are neutralized; Charter Protocol designates Anchor BLACK STAR.

THEMATIC SYNTHESIS:
Anchor has crossed from a fragmented individual to a conscious actor shaping reality. The choice to spare the Seedling was an act of sacred identification. He has accumulated responsibilities and titles. The story is no longer about finding a self, but about deciding what the self he has forged will do. The soul's fate is now a strategic decision.

